{"word":"G3809 - παιδεία - paideía - pahee-di'-ah - Chastening","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παιδεία</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>paideía"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>pahee-di'-ah"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Chastening"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"போதனை படிப்பிக்குதல், சிட்சை - பெண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"training and education, chastisement"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Feminine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (பெண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> From <a href=\"#/G3811 - παιδεύω - paideúō - pahee-dyoo'-o/3811\">G3811</a>; <i>tutorage</i>, that is, <i>education</i> or <i>training</i>; by implication disciplinary <i>correction:</i> - chastening, chastisement, instruction, nurture."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3807 - παιδαγωγός - paidagōgós - pahee-dag-o-gos'/3807\">G3807</a>, <a href=\"#/G3809 - παιδεία - paideía - pahee-di'-ah/3809\">G3809</a>, <a href=\"#/G3810 - παιδευτής - paideutḗs - pahee-dyoo-tace'/3810\">G3810</a>, <a href=\"#/G3811 - παιδεύω - paideúō - pahee-dyoo'-o/3811\">G3811</a>, <a href=\"#/G521 - ἀπαίδευτος - apaídeutos - ap-ah'-ee-dyoo-tos/521\">G521</a>"}]}